data.description: Beautiful open plan home with lots of upgrades. 4 bedroom 3 full bathrooms, Plus an office and a big play room that can be used as a 6 bedroom. Tile floor down stairs and new carpet upstairs. Formal living and dining room. Huge family room with a cozy fireplace. Amazing kitchen with an island, granite countertops, lots of cabinets, appliances and refrigerator included. Primary bedroom suite with a slide door and a nice balcony. Primary bathroom has a dual sink, separate shower, tile floor, garden tub, walk-in closet and another regular mirrored closet. All bedrooms have mini blinds. Down stairs has a bedroom with tile floor and mirrored closet. The downstairs bathroom has a tile floor and a window. The back yard has block fences, a shed, patio and playground. 3 car garage and RV access. New interior fresh paint and all the eaves outside of the house. Water softener. Paid solar panels. Security system. New heater. Big screen TV included. Washer and dryer included. Nest enabled thermostat. Down stairs laundry room. Dual AC units. You must see this gorgeous house before it is gone!
